    <item>
      <title>特朗普不断谈论伊朗的“核尘埃”。它是什么？</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/23/us/politics/trump-iran-nuclear-dust-uranium.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首先，它不是灰尘。这是伊朗储存的近乎炸弹级的铀，储存在与水肺氧气瓶大小相当的大罐中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/23/us/politics/trump-iran-nuclear-dust-uranium.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 22:13:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
